n=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ifc1665702608950.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ifc1665702608950.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ifc1665702608950.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ifc1665702608950\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Component </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__component_312401\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Component is a Main Development Object that defines an executable part of an\n      application. It defines the data structure used to access data, the layout (if applicable)\n      used to present it, and the actions used to modify, validate, and store data. </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__p_d95336e1_d95337e1_d95338e1\">Although components are always defined as a specific\n         type, such as a Dynamic Server Page or a Service, they share the same namespace, so names\n         of components must be unique for all components, not just for a specific type of\n         component.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__p_d95339e1_d95340e1_d95341e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dhu1704688959391.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dhu1704688959391.html\" title=\"Uniface application components are interchangeable software modules that handle application processing. They are technology-independent, so compiled components can be run on any operating system.\">Components</a>.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__topic_d63597e1_d63598e1_d63599e1_d63600e1_d63601e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d643016e66\"> Characteristics </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__image_id2_gcn_mwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/component.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">cpt</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yth1665702550544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yth1665702550544.html\" title=\"A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity.\">Component Entity</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wyt1665702609153.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyt1665702609153.html\" title=\"A Label is a Development Object that contains text that appears on a presentation component. Labels have properties, but most cannot be set dynamically.\">Label</a>,\n                              <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"srw1665702550375.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/srw1665702550375.html\" title=\"A Main Development Object is a Development Object that has no parent object, is maintained using a dedicated editor, and can be saved and exported as a single unit, with all its children.\">Main Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cdy1665702688628.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cdy1665702688628.html\" title=\"A Dynamic Server Page is a Component that defines a web page that can be incrementally and dynamically updated at runtime.\">Dynamic Server Page</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jmi1665702688698.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jmi1665702688698.html\" title=\"A Static Server Page is a Component that defines a web page that is updated as a complete page at runtime.\">Static Server Page</a>,\n                              <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dww1665702582302.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dww1665702582302.html\" title=\"A Service is a Component that defines a business logic component, which provides processing that does not require user interaction.\">Service</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uhd1665702582378.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uhd1665702582378.html\" title=\"A Session Service is a Component that defines a business logic component for handling task-specific data processing for other components.\">Session Service</a>,\n                              <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mpc1665702582452.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mpc1665702582452.html\" title=\"An Entity Service is a Component that defines a business logic component that handles database I/O for a single entity on behalf of other components. It is typically used in a generated 3-tier application.\">Entity Service</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"euw1665702582150.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/euw1665702582150.html\" title=\"A Form is a stateful presentation Component that enables users to view and modify data in a Windows or character mode application.\">Form</a>,\n                              <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rvk1665702582227.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rvk1665702582227.html\" title=\"A Report is a Component that defines the content and layout of printed output of a Uniface application. It is not interactive and cannot be used to update the database.\">Report</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Runtime component, component signature</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">.js</span> and <span class=\"ph filepath\">.hts</span> files (depending\n                           on the component type)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Example URI:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ifc1665702608950__table_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">cpt:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__topic_d63602e1_d63603e1_d63604e1_d63605e1_d63606e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d643016e345\"> Specialization </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__p_d95348e1_d95349e1_d95350e1\">The Component is an abstract type that specializes\n            Main Development Object in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37601e1_d37602e1_d37603e1\">It can contain one or more Component Entities,\n               Labels, and Component Variables. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__topic_d63607e1_d63608e1_d63609e1_d63610e1_d63611e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d643016e361\"> Properties </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__p_d95354e1_d95355e1_d95356e1\">Object Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37604e1_d37605e1_d37606e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37607e1_d37608e1_d37609e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owq1665702585461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owq1665702585461.html\" title=\"Type of Development Object. Read only.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37610e1_d37611e1_d37612e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybn1665702585544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybn1665702585544.html\" title=\"Complete URI of the Development Object. Read only.\">Location</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37613e1_d37614e1_d37615e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37616e1_d37617e1_d37618e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ipc1665702585697.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ipc1665702585697.html\" title=\"Use this property to provide comments or instructions for the selected development object. You can use the toolbar and standard Windows keyboard shortcuts to format the text, copy and paste, and undo and redo edits.\">Documentation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__p_d95357e1_d95358e1_d95359e1\">Source Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37619e1_d37620e1_d37621e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cnn1665702762358.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cnn1665702762358.html\" title=\"Read-only property the records the date and time when the object was last modified. The value is set by Uniface.\">Date Modified</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__p_d95360e1_d95361e1_d95362e1\">Configuration Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37622e1_d37623e1_d37624e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wyl1665702688770.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyl1665702688770.html\" title=\"Specifies the library containing the global objects used by the component or application shell. If no library is specified, the library defined for the application shell is used. Otherwise, SYSTEM_LIBRARY is used as the default.\">Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37625e1_d37626e1_d37627e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dfn1665702688838.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dfn1665702688838.html\" title=\"This property determines whether the component is a modeled component.\">Is Modeled Component</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37628e1_d37629e1_d37630e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mwa1665702688914.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mwa1665702688914.html\" title=\"This property specifies the name of the modeled component from which this component is derived.\">Modeled Component</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__p_d95363e1_d95364e1_d95365e1\">Behavior Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37631e1_d37632e1_d37633e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"obc1665703043525.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/obc1665703043525.html\" title=\"Specifies the type of Uniface Component.\">Component Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37634e1_d37635e1_d37636e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qsg1665702688984.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qsg1665702688984.html\" title=\"Determines the degree to which data in the component can be edited and stored.\">Data Access</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37637e1_d37638e1_d37639e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ypq1665702689055.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ypq1665702689055.html\" title=\"Specifies whether the component definition is cached in memory.\">Component Behavior</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37640e1_d37641e1_d37642e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cik1665702689127.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cik1665702689127.html\" title=\"Sets the value of the &lt;$cmpStatemanagedBy&gt; constant, which specifies the mechanism used to save state information for the component.\">State Managed By</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37643e1_d37644e1_d37645e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xhw1665702689197.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xhw1665702689197.html\" title=\"Determines whether the component can run on a server without reference to global objects or a user interface. Valid values are T or F (default).\">Self-Contained</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__p_d95366e1_d95367e1_d95368e1\">Data I/O Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37646e1_d37647e1_d37648e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iku1665702689266.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iku1665702689266.html\" title=\"Name of the Keyboard Translation Table used to interpret field data upon input.\">Input Translation</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37649e1_d37650e1_d37651e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dbe1665702689335.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dbe1665702689335.html\" title=\"Name of the Keyboard Translation Table used to convert field data upon output.\">Output Translation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__p_d95369e1_d95370e1_d95371e1\">Presentation Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37652e1_d37653e1_d37654e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"myt1665702689407.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/myt1665702689407.html\" title=\"Title displayed in the window title bar or browser tab when the application shell, form, or server page is run. If no title is specified, the object name is displayed.\">Title</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__p_d95372e1_d95373e1_d95374e1\">Character Mode Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37655e1_d37656e1_d37657e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fel1665702689477.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fel1665702689477.html\" title=\"Number of header lines displayed at the top of the component in character mode. The remainder of the form is scrolled. No default.\">Header Length</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37658e1_d37659e1_d37660e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lma1665702689548.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lma1665702689548.html\" title=\"Determines whether the screen is cleared before and after running a form that runs another form. Applicable only when the form is run in character mode. True or False (Default).\">Clear?</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37661e1_d37662e1_d37663e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rmo1665702689618.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rmo1665702689618.html\" title=\"Determines whether a rectangular border is displayed around the form component's outer edge in character mode.\">Borderline</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37664e1_d37665e1_d37666e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ngp1665702689690.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ngp1665702689690.html\" title=\"Display the field in reversed highlighting. Applicable only to Unifields.\">Inverse</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37667e1_d37668e1_d37669e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"abx1665702689822.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/abx1665702689822.html\" title=\"Display the field as bold. Applicable only to Unifields.\">Bright</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37670e1_d37671e1_d37672e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lhp1665702689890.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lhp1665702689890.html\" title=\"Display the field as underlined. Applicable only to Unifields.\">Underline</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37673e1_d37674e1_d37675e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"avq1665702689959.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/avq1665702689959.html\" title=\"Apply blinking to the field. Applicable only to Unifields.\">Blink</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__topic_d63612e1_d63613e1_d63614e1_d63615e1_d63616e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d643016e666\"> Triggers and Operations </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37676e1_d37677e1_d37678e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kez1665702582531.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kez1665702582531.html\" title=\"Handles processing when an Accept request is received, usually with the intention of closing the component and keeping all changes made on it. This trigger is exposed as an operation in the component signature.\">trigger accept</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37679e1_d37680e1_d37681e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aag1665703130023.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aag1665703130023.html\" title=\"Trigger that reacts to the user's request to start over with a clean form.\">trigger clear</a> (Form) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37682e1_d37683e1_d37684e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"two1665703130263.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/two1665703130263.html\" title=\"Trigger that deletes all occurrences currently in the component, both in the external structure, and in the database. This is a very dangerous trigger—use it with extreme care!\">trigger erase</a> (Form) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37685e1_d37686e1_d37687e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jzq1665702665465.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jzq1665702665465.html\" title=\"Interactive trigger that responds to the form getting focus.\">trigger getFocus (Form)</a> (Form) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37688e1_d37689e1_d37690e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oxi1665702665543.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oxi1665702665543.html\" title=\"ProcScript module that responds to the form losing focus. It can be used to verify the data to ensure that it is complete or correct.\">trigger loseFocus (Form)</a> (Form) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37691e1_d37692e1_d37693e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xye1665702608643.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xye1665702608643.html\" title=\"Trigger that responds to a request for a menu in a desktop application.\">trigger menu</a> (Form) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37694e1_d37695e1_d37696e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hmh1665703130535.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hmh1665703130535.html\" title=\"Location for ProcScript that retrieves data from the database.\">trigger retrieve</a> (Form) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37697e1_d37698e1_d37699e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jno1665702661208.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jno1665702661208.html\" title=\"Trigger that retrieves the next occurrence in the database with a primary key value greater than the current one.\">trigger retrieveSequential</a> (Form) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37700e1_d37701e1_d37702e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hmn1665702683413.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hmn1665702683413.html\" title=\"System trigger that provides component-specific post-processing.\">trigger postActivate</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37703e1_d37704e1_d37705e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"muo1665702683268.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/muo1665702683268.html\" title=\"System trigger that provides component-specific pre-processing. It is required in web applications to recreate the component state.\">trigger preActivate</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37706e1_d37707e1_d37708e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ita1665703130455.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ita1665703130455.html\" title=\"Interactive trigger for responding to a print request.\">trigger print</a> (Form, Report) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37709e1_d37710e1_d37711e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sux1665703129629.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sux1665703129629.html\" title=\"Interactive trigger for responding to a request for a pulldown menu in a desktop application.\">trigger pullDown</a> (Form) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37712e1_d37713e1_d37714e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ghq1665702608876.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ghq1665702608876.html\" title=\"Reacts to asynchronous messages that come from outside the application.\">trigger receiveMessage</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37715e1_d37716e1_d37717e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jvb1665703130778.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jvb1665703130778.html\" title=\"Trigger that responds to a request to save (store) the data.\">trigger store</a> (Form) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37718e1_d37719e1_d37720e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qun1665702582075.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qun1665702582075.html\" title=\"Trigger that handles processing when a Quit request is received, usually with the intention of closing the component without saving any modifications made in it. This trigger is exposed as an operation in the component signature.\">trigger quit</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37721e1_d37722e1_d37723e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"niy1665702606431.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/niy1665702606431.html\" title=\"Trigger for responding to user-defined key sequences as defined in the Keyboard Translation Table (KTT) or defined in the usys.ini section named as userkeys.\">trigger userKey</a> (Form) </li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37724e1_d37725e1_d37726e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mkf1719505969039.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mkf1719505969039.html\" title=\"Default component operation, which is invoked by the activate statement.\">operation exec</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37727e1_d37728e1_d37729e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zye1719506814289.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zye1719506814289.html\" title=\"Defines the component behavior when a component instance is created with newinstance (or by activate when newinstance is executed implicitly).\">operation init</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37730e1_d37731e1_d37732e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cca1719502924085.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cca1719502924085.html\" title=\"Defines the component behavior for a contained DSP instance after it is attached to a parent DSP.\">operation attach</a> (DSP) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37733e1_d37734e1_d37735e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nbe1719505542495.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nbe1719505542495.html\" title=\"Defines the component behavior when a contained DSP component instance is detached from the parent DSP.\">operation detach</a> (DSP) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37736e1_d37737e1_d37738e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tcd1719504517290.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tcd1719504517290.html\" title=\"Defines the component behavior when a component instance is removed.\">operation cleanup</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37739e1_d37740e1_d37741e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tdr1719503726176.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tdr1719503726176.html\" title=\"Defines the behavior that should occur in response to an Accept request. If an Accept trigger is defined, it is exposed as the accept operation in the component signature.\">operation accept</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ifc1665702608950__li_d37742e1_d37743e1_d37744e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"icw1719507043571.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/icw1719507043571.html\" title=\"Defines the processing that should occur during a Quit request. If a quit trigger is defined in a component, it is exposed as the quit operation in the component signature.\">operation quit</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613674\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613674\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Component Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Component A Component is a Main Development Object that defines an executable part of an application. It defines the data structure used to access data, the layout (if applicable) used to present it, and the actions used to modify, validate, and store data. Although components are always defined as a specific type, such as a Dynamic Server Page or a Service, they share the same namespace, so names of components must be unique for all components, not just for a specific type of component. For more information, see Components . Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: cpt Main Development Object? Yes Part of: — Contains: Component Entity , Label , Property , Code Container Generalization: Main Development Object Specializations: Dynamic Server Page , Static Server Page , Service , Session Service , Entity Service , Form , Report Compilation Output: Runtime component, component signature .js and .hts files (depending on the component type) Example URI: cpt: ComponentName Specialization The Component is an abstract type that specializes Main Development Object in the following ways: It can contain one or more Component Entities, Labels, and Component Variables. Properties Object Properties: Name Type Location Description Documentation Source Properties: Date Modified Configuration Properties: Library Is Modeled Component Modeled Component Behavior Properties: Component Type Data Access Component Behavior State Managed By Self-Contained Data I/O Properties: Input Translation Output Translation Presentation Properties: Title Character Mode Properties: Header Length Clear? Borderline Inverse Bright Underline Blink Triggers and Operations trigger accept trigger clear (Form) trigger erase (Form) trigger getFocus (Form) (Form) trigger loseFocus (Form) (Form) trigger menu (Form) trigger retrieve (Form) trigger retrieveSequential (Form) trigger postActivate trigger preActivate trigger print (Form, Report) trigger pullDown (Form) trigger receiveMessage trigger store (Form) trigger quit trigger userKey (Form) operation exec operation init operation attach (DSP) operation detach (DSP) operation cleanup operation accept operation quit Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}